[ Upstream commit 66e900a3d225575c8b48b59ae1fe74bb6e5a65cc ]

The only part of atmel_spi_remove which needs to be atomic is hardware
reset.

atmel_spi_stop_dma calls dma_terminate_all and this needs interrupts
